subtitleNullable: Customer, employee and service subscription data created using Faker
descriptionNullable:
This synthetic dataset was create using Faker (https://faker.readthedocs.io/en/master/),

It contains four datasets:
- Customers
- Sales Representatives
- Subscriptions
- Customers (Cleaning)

These datasets can be merged together.

The last dataset was manually edited to include a few examples of unclean data. Try looking for these examples yourself or see the notebook section for a cleaning and EDA example (https://www.kaggle.com/code/nickkrikota/example-data-cleaning-and-eda).

See how this dataset was created (https://www.kaggle.com/code/nickkrikota/creating-a-synthetic-dataset-in-faker)
